      <p>The configuration file is to be written using our own Domain Specific Language, in the following code examples, all bold words are key words of the language. Every section is closed using the DSL's keyword <code>End</code>. The definition of the DSL is given using the BNF format and the visual diagram is available.</p>


      <h4 id="SG">1. Serious Game</h4>

